name: Vkmusicdownloadscript
body:
### Script for downloading all audio files (music) from your VK.com account
Script for downloading all music from VK.com. It is allow to just open your VK.com audio page, scroll bottom to open all supposed downloaded musics and run this script to download all audio files from the page.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
